{"tid":789530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★一批內地苦主報警稱受騙投資倫敦金","createTime":"2018-08-22T10:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T21:51:26.000Z","uid":19454,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"54c171e4c3f7edfa288fa849f21b06f84bb61eda","tid":789530,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:10:09.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一批來自內地的苦主報警，聲稱受騙投資倫敦金等項目，損失達4億人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n苦主來自內地29個省市自治區，在前立法會議員王國興陪同下，到灣仔警署報案。<br />\n<br />\n他們稱，早前透過網上通訊程式結識了懷疑騙徒，對方最初教他們炒股票，一段時間後，推薦他們投資倫敦金，在本港的公司開設戶口，其後有人投資失利，有部分戶口失效，未能聯絡到有關的負責人，損失金錢。<br />\n<br />\n他們聲稱總數達4億人民幣，涉及本港6間金融公司，要求警方介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=317541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D317541&d=rlXUku49MyaB5TbjwnmeDNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=1d578e5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D317541&h=ef7d384d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=317541</a>"},{"pid":"40e4830b52f29216cfb5af369f503e279bfb6da2","tid":789530,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e554de826153356c7cca4f175fed8ce85c0099a","tid":789530,"uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/22/181139_146b46087cbb919bf8e14c6b97da0405.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F181139_146b46087cbb919bf8e14c6b97da0